{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"毛泽东思想万岁（对口词）","authors":["广州部队海上文化工作队"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":9,"day":28}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"编者的话：为了庆祝我们伟大的中华人民共和国成立十七周年，广大的业余文艺工作者和专业文艺团体，创作了许多歌唱我们敬爱的领袖毛主席、歌颂伟大的战无不胜的毛泽东思想的文艺节目。这些节目，表达了全国人民和全世界革命人民无限热爱毛主席，无限崇拜毛泽东思想的心情。革命的文艺是为无产阶级政治服务的，是为工农兵服务的，突出无产阶级政治，就是突出毛泽东思想。革命文艺为无产阶级政治服务，就要歌颂毛泽东思想。革命文艺要为工农兵服务，就要歌唱我们心中的红太阳毛主席，就要歌颂我们的命根子毛泽东思想。这里选登几个业余和专业文艺工作团体创作的节目。让我们同声歌唱伟大领袖毛主席，热情歌颂伟大的毛泽东思想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想万岁（对口词）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广州部队海上文化工作队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广州部队海上文化工作队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战旗飞扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海翻腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲震荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉的毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界各地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的人民战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓坏了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵略豺狼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胆战心慌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国强盗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疯狂叫嚷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想用战争威胁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓倒我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——那是作梦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想用恶毒诽谤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤立我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——那是妄想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意气风发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗志昂扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了祖国的富强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了人类的解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火海敢跨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山敢上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是最强大的武器；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指引着胜利的方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭着它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们打下江山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭着它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们巩固国防。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看大江南北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看长城内外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家学“毛选”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处歌声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民肩并肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产、练兵忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山上赤卫队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振臂欢呼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华儿女多奇志；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔山下自卫军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举枪高唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不爱红装爱武装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青纱帐里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命后代舞红缨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰子树下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑嫂月下守海防。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘胡兰的妹妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨亮手中钢刀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘老庄的青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿上绿色军装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琼崖纵队的老战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威风凛凛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活捉美国飞行员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁战士麦贤得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身负重伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持痛打蒋匪帮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的中国人民解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举红旗守边疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮抬起头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子弹推上膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援越南亲兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备痛打万恶的美国狼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国际主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们应尽的义务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们崇高的理想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的朋友遍天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想照四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向南望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贤良江边炮火飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越南儿女打胜仗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步枪打飞贼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮轰飞机场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是陷阱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地是尖桩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬寸步难行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军越打越坚强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向东望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富士山下歌声壮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本要独立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚回去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚回去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反美怒涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一浪高一浪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向西望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲丛林里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火高万丈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美洲山谷中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声震天响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挣断锁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起胸膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举大刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞长矛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"占村庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋地雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸桥梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓得约翰逊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭爹又喊娘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向北望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修正主义者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸奴才相。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向杀人犯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈膝投降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对革命者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肆意诽谤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可耻的叛徒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难逃法网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒火满腔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反帝反修"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指引着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的方向！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用世界的乡村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包围世界的城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用人民战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把旧世界推翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用人民战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把帝国主义埋葬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界无产者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同声欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界革命者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放声歌唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是当代的列宁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是世界的希望；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是英雄的旗手；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人类的太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用毛泽东思想武装起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百战百胜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下无敌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用毛泽东思想武装起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身是胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如铁如钢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗，战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打倒美国侵略者；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进，前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接人类的解放！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁！万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的人民战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁！万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉的毛泽东思想！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"捍卫毛泽东思想工人赤卫队上海总部（赤卫队）","type":"人物"},{"name":"人民战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"无产阶级国际主义","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}